* Data Relationships\nand Value Sampling
** Table relationships
***_ Unity Catalog foreign keys used auto
***_ Define joins in knowledge store if missing
***_ Specify Many-to-one, one-to-many etc.
** Value sampling
***_ Collects example values from columns
***_ Matches user prompts to real data values
***_ "California" → state code "CA"
** Value dictionaries
***_ For categorical columns
***_ Status codes, categories, regions
***_ Up to 1,024 values per column
***_ Up to 120 columns in space
***_ Refresh as data changes
@endmindmap
